// 首なし美人亭初イベント・マーくん加入

＊首なし美人亭では「冒険者の編成」ができます.個性ある冒険者たちでうまくパーティを組み、戦闘を有利に
すすめましょう.

Also, while Sol's physique is small, the number
of adventurers that can be carried at once is
limited. As she grows, her physique will become
larger, and the number of adventurers she can
carry will increase.

Also, in the rumors, new quests may arise and
useful hints may be brought up. Let's check
frequently!

\n<Bar owner>Right now, you can hire adventurers who are
available. Once hired, you can organize them into
a party at any time. However, you can only
organize up to three people in Sol-chan's party at
the moment.

\n<Bar owner>It's customary to give a certain amount of
advance payment to hire, but... it's not always
the case that ability and employment fees match.
Just because it's expensive doesn't necessarily
mean they're skilled adventurers.

\n<Bar owner>As time passes and you complete requests, you'll
be able to hire more adventurers. Don't rush too
much.
//　イスクさんとドラゴンカインド

＊By performing the Dragonkind ritual, adventurers
will be temporarily or permanently strengthened!

You can perform the Dragonkind ritual by visiting
the \i[7]\c[2]cheap inn\c[0] in Rukurea Village,
but it will require a considerable amount of
money... or perhaps quite a bit.

Let's perform the ritual strategically and
strengthen ourselves!
//　ウェイン＆セレスイベント

\n<Bar owner>Oh, Sol-chan... There's an adventurer here who
wants to meet you...

\n<Ninja>.........I'm Hayagake. I heard there's a
fledgling golden dragon around here... If you need
my strength, you should hire me.

Sol and the others ended up working at the bar, as
if they had remembered it from time to time!

\n<Bar owner>By the way, it seems that there have been rumors
of kidnappings in this neighborhood. They say
they're taking away cute kids and selling them.

\n<Bar owner>Don't think it's safe just because Sol is a
dragon, okay? It's dangerous if she wanders around
there alone.

I'm counting on you, miss.

information from the adventurer who recently
returned, but it seems that there is an entrance
to the underground world... the Underworld, in
this vicinity.

guild seems to want an investigation. I'm counting
on you.

village.
